Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.57,0:46:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并告诉它该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.40,0:46:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它播放
